headline: Tariffs Aren't O'Reilly's Biggest Problem, This Is
summary: O'Reilly Automotive sells auto parts, which are often made in foreign countries.  O'Reilly appears to believe it has a handle on this rising cost, but still hinted that it was a work in progress.  O'Reilly Automotive (NASDAQ: ORLY) is a fast-growing auto parts retailer.
